# Mind

A “personal growth” app

## Prerequisites

* Composer
* PHP
* NodeJS ^18 and NPM
* MySql

# TO RUN BACKEND

Create a mysql user with the following configuration:

DB_DATABASE=mind
DB_PASSWORD=Kreissibelius-77

Create a database with the same name and grant all privileges

On Backend folder:
1) composer i
2) composer update
1) php artisan migrate
2) php artisan serve

# TO RUN FRONTEND IN DEV

On Frontend folder:
1) npm install
2) npm run dev